{"tid":1743893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【抗暴之戰】天水圍頭中催淚彈孤兒仍危殆","createTime":"2019-11-21T12:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T16:56:20.000Z","uid":13663,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"0e0acf1de66876b4fe4be17b48cfd301c4896471","tid":1743893,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:10:12.000Z","msg":"15歲少年傅同學11月13日晚在天水圍被防暴警發射的催淚彈擊中頭部重創，即晚入院進行開腦手術後，情況未見好轉。傅同學父母雙亡，與兄長雙依為命並由叔父照顧，今日再有網上消息傳出，傅同學病情仍然未見好轉，求網民集氣支持；協助傅同學的基督教信義會青少年服務總監竺永洪向《蘋果》表示，傅同學仍然危殆，手術後一直於深切治療部留醫。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，11月13日晚上約9時，逾百巿民包圍天水圍警署，並在附近街道設路障及磚頭陣，期間向警署投擲汽油彈，警署停車場一度火光熊熊。警方其後在警署高層向外發射催淚彈，短時間內發射至少50枚，未幾防暴警衝出向人群發射催淚彈驅散；至晚上10時許，傅同學在天水圍新北江商場對開，被防暴警發射的催淚彈擊中頭部昏迷，義務救護員進行急救再送院。"},{"pid":"fe5ae9f5bfa1ebca1da02b0e187e5051fd956e8f","tid":1743893,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:10:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191121/60291858\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191121%2F60291858&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameK0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=5c48694b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191121%2F60291858&h=8317ad77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191121/60291858</a>"},{"pid":"69aefa2c1e2bd94b446a0228ca5f391a99cc3e37","tid":1743893,"uid":20727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:11:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10e03f75c682c5ac4c080c191cfb09c93702db7b","tid":1743893,"uid":165482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:16:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95fc5abeba7b6abf1caa9126e9670b1ece41cad9","tid":1743893,"uid":262116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:17:41.000Z","msg":"咁賤既把口 叫人孤兒"},{"pid":"59